{"tid":1950670,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持Rthk] 鏗鏘集：抗疫日夜","createTime":"2020-03-30T12:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T05:47:39.000Z","uid":41818,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a35ebebf1af43b871c07e97a326ff5124ba155ba","tid":1950670,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/T27dONnqZDU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT27dONnqZDU&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2apJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=912a7c42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T27dONnqZDU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情蔓延全球，3月中開始本港輸入個案急增，引發新一輪本地社區傳播。東區醫院自2月初開始，接收了大量本地群組確診個案，包括打邊爐家族和北角佛堂群組。《鏗鏘集》自2月開始記錄他們的抗疫日夜，了解醫院由上至下如何應對這場疫戰。隔離病房醫護和管理層，他們在這段期間經歷如何？疫情危機乍現，他們又可以如何應對？"},{"pid":"0af556179be205deb3cc6e293f305979ba43fc31","tid":1950670,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"有時外遊撚咁多香港人屌唔係無原因，為人為己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264a19fd1e08aa3b101187b964f0b6ab01093a93","tid":1950670,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04fa90de99117942bd4c53a0342ee4855d330b8","tid":1950670,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c8c5d2541da7a9f1b71311a0842c572ea3566e","tid":1950670,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04fa90de99117942bd4c53a0342ee4855d330b8","tid":1950670,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\